                        The rate of premium and Extended Insurance Benefits is reviewed and decided, based on actuarial calculation for the amount and period of cover. The amount of Insurance Cover and period of cover,
                        applicable to members, who are granted Extended Insurance Cover, is as mentioned in the Extended Insurance Certificate issued to each member at the time of their retirement / discharge. For persons who joined the scheme
